{
  "stem": "2684.2",
  "chunk_idx": 12,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I was with a childhood friend of mine who never came back.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Mengele pulled us apart.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "He went to the left, I went to the right.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "I will tell that about later.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And about another four or five friends of mine who we got friendly with the-- with the orphanage boys, we stayed in one corner, and all the other boys been scattered around.",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And we existed there till Thursday.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] Existence means that you didn't have to do anything.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "You just walked around, talked.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "Adults didn't talk much about it, because we were very little.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "They talked amongst each other.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "We heard something.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "But anyway, in Thursday, the brickwork had a, a, a railway, because the brick had to be delivered from somewhere.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "So they had a railway line, and they brought in a, a, a whole set of freight carriages, which is-- in Hungary meant cows, sheep, whatever it is.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "And they put us in till was full, till seams.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "I think so.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "That's the correct word.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "And they locked up the wagons.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "Came the locomotive, and my trip to Auschwitz begun.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "Which meant that they only opened in [INAUDIBLE], which is already in Czechoslovakia-- no food, no water, no nothing.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "And in [INAUDIBLE], they already took out about six or seven elderly people who were just about dying.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "Some of them went from thirst, some of them went banana in the wagon, which means they went cuckoo, they went mad.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "So they took them off.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "And I never forgot the guy who gave us to the Germans.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "And that was one of the head Gendarmes in Hungary.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "He was the boss of this Gendarme organization.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "And if I'm not wrong, his name was [?",
      "word_count": 9
    }
  ],
